Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nego, šta bih trebao da stavim ovde?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:04.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Na kraju krajeva, ne znam šta to SOS Brigada treba da radi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:06.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Imaš li nešto što hoćeš da staviš na sajt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:09.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ništa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:14.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nije da me brine, ali...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:17.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...ona ide na časove, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dovraga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:33.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Počeće časovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:37.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Drži.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:39.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozajmiću ti ovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Još uvek imam neke slutnje...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:02.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...pa zašto onda nastavljam da idem do sobe kluba?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:03.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zašto li...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Da li je ovo moć navike?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Baš bezveze.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:09.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Poz!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:14.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bolje pitanje. Da li je njima dvema toliko dosadno?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mada ni ja nisam bolji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Gde je Suzumija?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:19.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemam pojma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:22.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Već je bila otišla tokom šestog časa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:25.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Možda je otišla da iznudi još opreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:30.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoću li morati ponovo da učinim nešto kao juče...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne brini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:34.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sledeći put ću učiniti sve u svojoj moći da sprečim to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stvarno?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hvala ti!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Računaću na tebe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:41.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Možeš da računaš na mene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jahoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Prvo je ovo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:55.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Objava politike SOS Brigade...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I ovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:01.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-ta-ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:04.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Delićemo letke obučene u ovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:05.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Gde?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:06.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kod glavne kapije.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:09.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Trebalo bi da bude puno učenika koji kreću kući sada.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:09.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:10.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Šta nosimo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:12.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nisam mislila na tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:14.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru će nositi ovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:14.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Da?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Zečica!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ovaj... Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Šta je...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:19.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajde!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:20.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Presvlači se, presvlači se!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:21.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne želim!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:22.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tišina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:23.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Skidaj to! Skidaj to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:25.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:26.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Suzumija!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:27.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Šta to radiš!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:28.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:29.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne gledaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajde! Radi što ti kažem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:34.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Eto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:39.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Skidaj sve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:45.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:47.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bar me pusti da se sama skinem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:51.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Možeš da uđeš!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kao da je neki zli feudalni vlastelin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:58.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Šta misliš?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:11:01.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ovo će biti savršeno za privlačenje pažnje, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:03.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolje reći upijaće pažnju...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:04.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A Nagato?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogla sam da kupim samo dva.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:09.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kupila sam ceo komplet, pa je bilo skupo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:10.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Gde prodaju ove stvari?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:12.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Naručila sam ih na internetu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:13.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tako znači.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa, idemo onda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:17.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajde, Mikuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:22.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Idemo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:30.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Da budem iskren, ne mogu da se nagledam toga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Moja strast divlja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:40.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Št—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pobogu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:52.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Još su ostale tople.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sve je toplo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:01.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Objava politike SOS Brigade...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:05.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naša SOS Brigada traga za misterijama sveta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:09.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ljudi koji su iskusili nešto misteriozno u prošlosti...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:13.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ljudi koji su se skoro sreli sa misterijama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:16.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ljudi koji nameravaju da imaju misteriozno iskustvo u budućnosti...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:19.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ako ima takvih ljudi, dođite da popričate sa nama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:22.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rešićemo vaše probleme na mestu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ali normalna misterija neće biti dovoljna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:28.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To mora biti misterija koja će nas zadiviti!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:29.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zapamtite to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:33.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mislim da počinjem da shvatam svrhu ove brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:40.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Besna sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:42.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Šta je sa tim glupim nastavnicima?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:43.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Prava su smetnja! Smetnja!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:46.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeli bilo nekih problema?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Više od toga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:49.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nismo podelile ni pola letaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:51.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...a nastavnici su nam rekli da prekinemo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ko oni misle da su!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ako dve zečice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:56.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...krenu da dele letke ispred glavne kapije...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...ljudi koji nisu nastavnici će dotrčavati.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:00.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru je počela da jeca...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:03.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja sam odvučena kod učeničkog savetnika...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:05.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Čak je i onaj odbojkaški moron Okabe bio doveden!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:08.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Verovatno su bili na ivici suza.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:09.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Čoveče...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Završavamo za danas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:13.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Raspuštanje!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Koliko dugo ćeš da plačeš!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:17.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajde!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Presvlači se!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:28.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kjon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:32.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako budem upropašćena za brak...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:34.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...hoćeš li me uzeti?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:41.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Šta bih trebao da kažem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:42.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Asahina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:45.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sa leđa izgledaš kao student koji nije uspeo da se upiše na fakultet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:50.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ili kancelarijski radnik koji je kupio kuću iznad svojih mogućnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:51.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Čekaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:53.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ti ćeš da me zoveš tako?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:59.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sledeći dan, ime Suzumije Haruhi je nadmašilo prostu ozloglašenost...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:02.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...i postalo opšte znanje svih učenika.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:05.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Čoveče, Kjon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:10.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Konačno si postao jedan od Suzumijinih veselih drugara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:10.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ućuti.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:13.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ono što je bilo još gore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:16.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...je što su moje i Asahinino ime postali povezani sa njenim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:19.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Juče sam baš bio iznenađen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:22.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mislim, kod glavne kapije su stajale zečice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:23.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Druga je bila ona drugakinja, Asahina, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:29.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sada imate pažnju cele škole na sebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Šta je ta SOS Brigada?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:35.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitaj Suzumiju.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja nemam pojma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:38.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A ni ne želim da znam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:41.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Izgleda da se zabavljate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:43.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ali mislim da je to bilo malo previše.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:48.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Asahina je bila odsutna iz škole danas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:51.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Zašto nikada ne dobijamo mejlove?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:52.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Posle svog tog publiciteta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:56.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nema nikoga ko je dovoljno radoznao da se javi pošto je video tvoj publicitet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:59.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doduše, priznaću da si nas učinila poznatim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:01.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:03.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeli Mikuru odsutna danas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:05.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Možda se više nikada ne vrati.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nadam se da neće biti istraumirana od toga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:10.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Čak sam joj donela i novo odelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:12.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nosi ga sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:14.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Naravno! I ja ću ga nositi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:17.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ali nije zabavno kada Mikuru nije tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:19.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mogla bi da pitaš Nagato da ga obuče.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:22.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Verovatno bi to učinila bez žalbi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A imam i osećaj da mi ne bi smetalo da to vidim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:30.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,SOS Brigada je tek osnovana a već sedimo ne radeći ništa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:33.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitam se da li se svi suzdržavaju.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:34.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Žele da sačuvaju misteriju za sebe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:36.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hej, Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koga kod da pitaš...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:40.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...reći će, "Ne, nema ih".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:46.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nema šanse da bi ova državna srednja škola imala misterije sakrivene po ćoškovima.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:47.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Razumeš, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:50.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Istina je da razumeš, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:53.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Samo što nemaš gde drugde da izduvaš frustracije svoje mladosti...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:57.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...pa te ta uznemirenost vodi drugačijom stazom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:59.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Osvesti se više.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:02.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zašto ne nađeš nekog zgodnog momka i zajedno se vraćate kući iz škole...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:05.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...ili idete da gledate filmove nedeljom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:08.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I pridruži se nekom sportskom klubu i luduj koliko hoćeš.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:12.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tebe bi odmah načinili stalnim članom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:12.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Idem kući!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:22.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:24.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I ja idem kući.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:26.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesi li je pročitao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:27.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pročitao šta?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:30.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Knjigu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne, ne još...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:34.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Da je vratim?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:37.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nije potrebno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:37.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ali čoveče...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:40.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ona nije jedna od pričljivijih...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:42.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pročitaj je danas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:45.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Čim se vratiš kući.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Razumem.
